```

## Dataset Attribution

This project uses datasets for Indonesian hate speech detection. If you use this project, please ensure proper attribution to the original dataset creators and follow their licensing terms.

## Ethical Use

This software is provided for research and educational purposes. Users are responsible for ensuring ethical use of hate speech detection systems and should consider:

1. Potential biases in the training data
2. Cultural and linguistic nuances in hate speech detection
3. Privacy concerns when processing user-generated content
4. The impact of automated content moderation on free speech

## Disclaimer

The authors and contributors of this project do not take responsibility for any misuse of this software or any harm that may result from its use. This tool is intended to assist in research and development of hate speech detection systems, not to make final decisions about content moderation without human oversight.
